{
  "title": "解决Sublime Text 3在GBK编码下的中文乱码问题",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"exp-content-body exp-brief-step\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><div class=\"exp-content-listblock\" style=\"position: relative;\"><div class=\"content-listblock-text\"><p style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px;\">Sublime Text 3是我最喜欢的代码编辑器，没有之一，因为她的性感高亮代码配色，更因为它的小巧，但是它默认不支持GBK的编码格式，因此打开GBK的代码文件，如果里面有中文的话，就会乱码</p></div><div class=\"content-listblock-media\"><div class=\"content-listblock-image clearfix exp-image-center\" style=\"zoom: 1; padding-left: 340px; float: left; text-align: center;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/fc07f98972ee0a12fee51943.html?picindex=1\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left; margin-left: -250px;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Sublime Text 3在GBK编码下的中文乱码问题\" src=\"quiver-image-url/298DA3680F63149A1F3D2F178167FAB3.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 500px; overflow: hidden;\" width=\"375\" height=\"233\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div><div class=\"exp-brief-clear\" style=\"clear: both; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\"><a name=\"section-2\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 100, 179);\"></a>工具/原料<div class=\"audio-wp audio-wp-2\" data-text=\"\" data-for=\"\" data-index=\"1\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 4px; color: rgb(81, 154, 242); cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1; vertical-align: middle;\"><span class=\"audio-inner\" style=\"display: inline-block; height: 20px;\"><span class=\"audio-icon\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 20px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/audio/img/audio_5b24a3c.png?__sprite); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"></span><span class=\"audio-icon-2\" style=\"position: relative; display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 20px; margin-left: 3px; background-image: url(&quot;//exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/audio/img/a1_c12da1b.png?__sprite&quot;);\"></span><span class=\"audio-icon-3\" style=\"position: relative; display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 20px; margin-left: -2px; background-image: url(&quot;//exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/audio/img/a2_0c36615.png?__sprite&quot;);\"></span></span><span class=\"desc\" style=\"position: relative; top: -5px; margin-left: 2px;\"></span></div></h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ul class=\"exp-content-unorderlist \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/content/detail/img/unsortlist_a3c9345.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><div class=\"content-list-text\">Sublime Text 3</div></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\"><a name=\"section-3\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 100, 179);\"></a>方法/步骤<div class=\"audio-wp audio-wp-2\" data-text=\"\" data-for=\"\" data-index=\"2\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 4px; color: rgb(81, 154, 242); cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1; vertical-align: middle;\"><span class=\"audio-inner\" style=\"display: inline-block; height: 20px;\"><span class=\"audio-icon\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 20px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/audio/img/audio_5b24a3c.png?__sprite); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"></span><span class=\"audio-icon-2\" style=\"position: relative; display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 20px; margin-left: 3px; background-image: url(&quot;//exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/audio/img/a1_c12da1b.png?__sprite&quot;);\"></span><span class=\"audio-icon-3\" style=\"position: relative; display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 20px; margin-left: -2px; background-image: url(&quot;//exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/audio/img/a2_0c36615.png?__sprite&quot;);\"></span></span><span class=\"desc\" style=\"position: relative; top: -5px; margin-left: 2px;\"></span></div></h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ol class=\"exp-conent-orderlist\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left: 2px dotted rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/img-baidu-com/step_ol_bg_e53cfaf.png); visibility: hidden; top: -8px !important; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">大家如果是在官网下载的Sublime Text 3，那么首先需要安装一个</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Package&nbsp;Control包，这是一个用来安装其他插件的包，不管装什么插件，首先要先装这个包才行</p></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-2\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left: 2px dotted rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/img-baidu-com/step_ol_bg_e53cfaf.png); visibility: hidden; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">按ctrl+~快捷键，调出一个小文本款，然后粘贴以下代码：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">import&nbsp;urllib.request,os,hashlib;&nbsp;h&nbsp;=&nbsp;'7183a2d3e96f11eeadd761d777e62404'&nbsp;+&nbsp;'e330c659d4bb41d3bdf022e94cab3cd0';&nbsp;pf&nbsp;=&nbsp;'Package&nbsp;Control.sublime-package';&nbsp;ipp&nbsp;=&nbsp;sublime.installed_packages_path();&nbsp;urllib.request.install_opener(&nbsp;urllib.request.build_opener(&nbsp;urllib.request.ProxyHandler())&nbsp;);&nbsp;by&nbsp;=&nbsp;urllib.request.urlopen(&nbsp;'http://sublime.wbond.net/'&nbsp;+&nbsp;pf.replace('&nbsp;',&nbsp;'%20')).read();&nbsp;dh&nbsp;=&nbsp;hashlib.sha256(by).hexdigest();&nbsp;print('Error&nbsp;validating&nbsp;download&nbsp;(got&nbsp;%s&nbsp;instead&nbsp;of&nbsp;%s),&nbsp;please&nbsp;try&nbsp;manual&nbsp;install'&nbsp;%&nbsp;(dh,&nbsp;h))&nbsp;if&nbsp;dh&nbsp;!=&nbsp;h&nbsp;else&nbsp;open(os.path.join(&nbsp;ipp,&nbsp;pf),&nbsp;'wb'&nbsp;).write(by)</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/fc07f98972ee0a12fee51943.html?picindex=2\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Sublime Text 3在GBK编码下的中文乱码问题\" src=\"quiver-image-url/C41875E29265A6A83634BF778270D502.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 500px; overflow: hidden;\" width=\"375\" height=\"154\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-3\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left: 2px dotted rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/img-baidu-com/step_ol_bg_e53cfaf.png); visibility: hidden; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">安装完后重启下Sublime Text 3，在perferences选项一栏下面就会多了个Package Control</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/fc07f98972ee0a12fee51943.html?picindex=3\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Sublime Text 3在GBK编码下的中文乱码问题\" src=\"quiver-image-url/A0AC4D9F37A269BE16BAFFF69B2B60A2.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 500px; overflow: hidden;\" width=\"375\" height=\"213\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-4\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left: 2px dotted rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/img-baidu-com/step_ol_bg_e53cfaf.png); visibility: hidden; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">点击Package Control，上面会出来一个输入框，我们输入install，就会自动有提示那个install package，我们点击一下install package，输入框会消失，稍等一下又会弹出个输入框。</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/fc07f98972ee0a12fee51943.html?picindex=4\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Sublime Text 3在GBK编码下的中文乱码问题\" src=\"quiver-image-url/690E84D1EA9DF344D9097C01F0504C19.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 500px; overflow: hidden;\" width=\"375\" height=\"153\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-5\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left: 2px dotted rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/img-baidu-com/step_ol_bg_e53cfaf.png); visibility: hidden; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">这时我们可以输入需要安装的那个插件包（ConvertToUTF8）了</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/fc07f98972ee0a12fee51943.html?picindex=5\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Sublime Text 3在GBK编码下的中文乱码问题\" src=\"quiver-image-url/9D85CE6C0FDB7F054D298337AD93154A.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 500px; overflow: hidden;\" width=\"375\" height=\"260\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-6\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left: 2px dotted rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/img-baidu-com/step_ol_bg_e53cfaf.png); visibility: hidden; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">安装好这个包之后，重启下Sublime Text 3，就可以发现其打开GBK编码格式下的中文也不会乱码了。</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/fc07f98972ee0a12fee51943.html?picindex=6\" log=\"type:20150831,pos:enter_step,expGroup:G0\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"解决Sublime Text 3在GBK编码下的中文乱码问题\" src=\"quiver-image-url/732A143828291E34711A3B4080AC9D50.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 500px; overflow: hidden;\" width=\"375\" height=\"265\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div><div class=\"last-item\" style=\"position: relative; height: 13px; margin-top: 5px;\"><span class=\"last-item-end\" style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); position: absolute; bottom: 0px; left: -48px; display: block;\">END</span></div></li></ol></div></div><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px; font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\"><a name=\"section-4\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 100, 179);\"></a>注意事项<div class=\"audio-wp audio-wp-2\" data-text=\"\" data-for=\"\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 4px; color: rgb(81, 154, 242); cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1; vertical-align: middle;\"><span class=\"audio-inner\" style=\"display: inline-block; height: 20px;\"><span class=\"audio-icon\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 20px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/audio/img/audio_5b24a3c.png?__sprite); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"></span><span class=\"audio-icon-2\" style=\"position: relative; display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 20px; margin-left: 3px; background-image: url(&quot;//exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/audio/img/a1_c12da1b.png?__sprite&quot;);\"></span><span class=\"audio-icon-3\" style=\"position: relative; display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 20px; margin-left: -2px; background-image: url(&quot;//exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/audio/img/a2_0c36615.png?__sprite&quot;);\"></span></span><span class=\"desc\" style=\"position: relative; top: -5px; margin-left: 2px;\"></span></div></h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ul class=\"exp-content-unorderlist \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/content/detail/img/unsortlist_a3c9345.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><div class=\"content-list-text\">首要条件是得先装package control</div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; background-image: url(file://exp.bdstatic.com/static/article/widget/content/detail/img/unsortlist_a3c9345.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><div class=\"content-list-text\">如果您觉得这篇经验有用的话，麻烦投上您宝贵的一票，当然您也可以收藏哦！</div></li></ul></div></div>"
